Date: Wed, 8 Apr 2026 17:20:00 -0300
Subject: [PATCH] lib: expose channel scope waveforms for host visualizers

Capture recent per-channel waveform history inside the replay core and expose
it through KSND_GetChannelScopeSamples() so host integrations can render live
channel scopes without depending on editor-only buffers.
---
